author: @2YOUNGWOO
text:
외국 팬들이 다 쯔위 예상하는데 저는 개인적으로 손코디 아니면 박회장 김감독(사나) 인것 같습니다.

1. 모조연은 사귄사이라 질투났을수도 있으나 죽이는거까지는 아닌것 같고 
2. 정포토는 영정사진 찍어준다는 말 하나가지고 아직 살인범이라 보기는 어려운거 같고
3. 임대표는 돈문제로 있어서나 문자 및 발자국일치도 수상하긴하나 아직 확실치 않고 
4. 유작가는 노트에 적힌게 뭔지 밝히지 않아 아직 모르고

이유로는 손코디는 일단 제일 마지막에 본 목격자이면서 과도라고는 하지만 칼과 약이 있었고 (물증)
김감독은 트러블이 있어서 말다툼으로 인해 확김에 살인했을 가능성이 있고 (심증)

박회장 모조연과 나가수가 사겼었다는 것을 알고 전직 약사 출신으로 독약을 만들었을 가능성 (심증) (근데 저라면 솔직히 모조연을 없애려 하지 않았을까 싶네요)

쯔위는 막내매니저로 악감정이 있는건지 아직 관련된 증거들이 많이 없고 그냥 시체를 보면서 웃은것 (심증) 밖에는 밝혀진것이 없어 다음화를 봐야 알수 있을 것 같네요

author: @BoP
text: The real meta game is guessing who is the culprit based on overarching events + member personalities. See they wouldn't pick Jihyo or Momo because of them being in the news a lot. They wouldn't pick Jeongyeon because she had a leave of absence. DaChaeTzu are the youngest so they wouldn't do that either. Nayeon is too obvious and they wouldn't tarnish Sana's bubbly persona. So it's gotta be Mina. They are gonna play into her mysterious and quiet side. Notice how they didn't give her a lot of screen time this episode. They are trying to make us forget about her character so it surprises us. I believe it's Mina.

author: @azusaharrison7985
text:
Sé que nadie va a leer esto :v
Pero yo NO sospecho de Mina, ya que las fotografías "difunto" pueden ser porque ella es la fotógrafa, y ella y Nagasu pudieron hablar sobre las fotografías del ALBUM, ya que el título de la canción es "death".
Tampoco sospecho de Chaeyoung, ya que se vería muy lógico, demasiado para ser verdad, como el cuchillo, siento que eso sólo es para desviar nuestra atención del verdadero asesino.
De las miembros que mas sospecho son:
Momo , ya que definitivamente el asesino tuvo o tiene sentimientos amorosos y obsesivos hacia Nagasu, y la carta con sangre dice "Se mío, o muere". Por lo tanto también sospecho de Nayeon y Jihyo,  Jihyo puede ser una fan obsesiva, ya que es la presidenta de su club de fans e incluso hizo un trámite para ser su manager, como si ella quisiera estar todo el tiempo con Nagasu y además se ve demasiado linda como para ser creíble :v. Momo es la exnovia de Nagasu, y como dice Sana , pudo haber sido por celos, PERO, su relación fue secreta, y cuando Nayeon mencionó que Momo sentía sentimientos por Nagasu, Jihyo no reaccionó bien, así que eso me hace sospechar más de Jihyo -_-.
Momo y Jihyo posibles yanderes :v
También sospecho de Sana , ya que ella es la directora de escenario, y se supone que ella debe revisar que esté en orden, ya que es la directora, y en el episodio anterior ella fue la última en llegar.
También sospecho de Nayeon, ya que en el primer episodio, cuando todas las chicas comenzaban a llegar y a presentar sus nombres,le preguntó a Tzuyu si ella sabía dónde estaba Nagasu, y en ese momento aún no se sabía que Nagasu ya había desaparecido, es como si Nayeon supiera lo que pasó antes que todos.
Hace un rato leí en los comentarios que pudo haber sido una estrategia de Nagasu, para atraer público y atención, ya que sus cuentas/dinero estaban bajando, así que puede que Nagasu esté vivo, y Nayeon, quién es el ¿Ceo?, Sabe de esto, ya que todo fue un plan. Por eso la canción desde el principio se llama "Death" , la fotógrafa le dijo que le tomaría fotos muerto, Chaeyoung lo vió, y Sana, la directora de sus escenario también ayudaron al plan. Lol xd.

author: @kshinichi2637
text:
Dahyun -She watches a lot Murd3r/Cri*me movies . She must've learned a lot of tricks after watching lots of Murd*r/Crime movies. The song title and what happened to Na Gasu is too coincidental, like it's planned beforehand, and her research about how the sales of the songs of the famous artists who dies goes up made it looked a lot more like it was really planned.

CEO Im -She said Na Gasu was the only artist in her company. But why is the company in such a huge deficit? Na Gasu was on a hiatus for years y'know. Does Na Gasu have something to do with the company being in that state? Does CEO Im loathe Na Gasu because of it. -Also, it's questionable why Na Gasu is her only artist. Maybe she's that obsessive freak that did something to Na Gasu who only wants Na Gasu for herself. If so, then the reason she murder*d Na Gasu must be because the huge problem Na Gasu made for the company and Na Gasu dating Momo (Momo said she and Na Gasu went out) 

President Park (Jihyo) -There are too many hints that leads to her. Like it was meant to mislead others. It's like the perpetrator knows that she's a big fan of Na Gasu and that she's a pharmacist. It's like the perpetrator wants to take adv4ntage of this. 

Showcase Director, Sana -I don't think it's Sana. As she said, they've spent nights and tired themselves for this showcase. And her, arguing with Na Gasu because of Na Gasu's opinion for the showcase just shows she is passionate/determined for the showcase. She wouldn't give so much effort for the showcase if she would just murd*r him in the end. If she is the perpetrator, she wouldn't mind arguing with Na Gasu. She would just let him be, take his opinions or what, because in the end, she will just murd*r him before the showcase starts.

Welp, this is only my opinion. How 'bout you? Who do you think is it?
